==生物 ==
[[File:Socotra_dragon_tree.JPG|缩略图]]的樹汁呈紅色<ref>{{cite journal|author=Becky Chung|title=World's Most Unique Places To Visit|url=http://www.forbes.com/2009/11/04/unique-vacations-travel-lifestyle-travel-adventure-tourism.html|journal=Forbes|date=2009-11-04|access-date=2017-09-05|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730101606/https://www.forbes.com/2009/11/04/unique-vacations-travel-lifestyle-travel-adventure-tourism.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。]]
该岛早在[[中新世|中新世]]就从大陆分离，因为拥有数量众多的本土特色植物，被称为印度洋上的[[加拉巴哥群島|加拉巴哥群島]]。

这座小岛已于2008年被列入[[世界自然遗产|世界自然遗产]]，上面生活着700多种极其罕见的动植物，其中三分之一在地球其他地方都看不到{{r|renmin2009}}，90%的爬行动物和95%的[[腹足綱|腹足綱]]物種也是岛上独有的。索科特拉岛有140多种鸟，其中10种是该岛独有的，例如索科特拉岛八哥、太阳鸟、彩旗、索岛栗翅椋鸟、鵐和金翅蜡嘴雀等。此外，索科特拉岛还有253种造礁珊瑚、730种沿岸鱼、300种螃蟹、龙虾和小虾。因此有“生物进化活博物馆”之称。

岛上最著名的物种是[[索科特拉龍血樹|龙血树]]，此外还有[[索科特拉野石榴|索科特拉野石榴]]<ref name="IUCN">{{IUCN2010|assessors=Miller, A.|year=2004|id=30404|title=Punica protopunica|version=2010.4|downloaded=2010-11-12}}</ref>。但是由于外来物种，尤其是[[山羊|山羊]]的不断繁殖，岛上的植物受到很大的威胁。<ref>{{cite web|title=奇幻索科特拉岛 地球上最像外星的地方|url=http://travel.ifeng.com/world/detail_2015_07/04/41071565_0.shtml|website=凤凰网|publisher=艺术中国|accessdate=2017-09-05|date=2015-07-04|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120023324/https://travel.ifeng.com/world/detail_2015_07/04/41071565_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
岛上曾发现公元前4000～前3000年石器文化古迹<ref>{{cite journal| last=Amirkhanov|first=K.A. |last2=Zhukov|first2=V.A.|last3=Naumkin|first3=V.V.|last4=Sedov|first4=A.V.|script-title=ru:Эпоха олдована открыта на острове Сокотра|journal=Pripoda|issue=7|year=2009|language=ru}}</ref>。根据岛上的记载，早在公元52年，岛民就已经在[[圣多马|圣多马]]的指引下皈依[[基督教|基督教]]<ref>{{cite book|last=Polo|first= Marco|title=The Travels of Marco Polo|url=https://archive.org/details/travelsofmarcopo0000polo_t1b0|others=Translated and introduction by Ronald Latham|publisher= Penguin Books|year=1958|pages=[https://archive.org/details/travelsofmarcopo0000polo_t1b0/page/296 296]–297| isbn =0-14-044057-7}}</ref> 。1507年，[[葡萄牙人|葡萄牙人]]来到岛上，帮助岛民摆脱了阿拉伯半岛上[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]国家的控制<ref>{{cite journal|last=Monteiro|first= Alexandre|title=Uma página dos Descobrimentos: a ilha de Socotorá no século XVI|language=pt|journal= National Geographic Portugal|date=June 2012|pages= 42–45}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vtZtMBLJ7GgC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1|title=Foundations of the Portuguese empire, 1415–1580|first=Bailey Wallys|last=Diffie|first2=George Davison|last2=Winius|page=233|year=1977|publisher=University of Minnesota Press|isbn=0-8166-0782-6|access-date=2017-09-05|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216224545/https://books.google.com/books?id=vtZtMBLJ7GgC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但是4年以后葡萄牙人离开该岛，使得岛民又重新沦为{{le|马赫里苏丹国|Mahra Sultanate}}的臣民<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=c788wWR_bLwC&pg=PA753&lpg=PA753|title=Late Antiquity: A Guide to the Postclassical World|first=Glen Warren|last=Bowersock|first2=Peter|last2=Brown|first3=Oleg|last3=Grabar|page=753|year=1999|publisher=Harvard University Press|isbn=0674511735|access-date=2017-09-05|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216224551/https://books.google.co.in/books?id=c788wWR_bLwC&pg=PA753&lpg=PA753|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1886年，同马赫里苏丹国一道归入[[英国|英国]]保护，属[[亚丁保护国|亚丁保护国]]，成为英国在印度洋上的重要基地<ref>{{cite book|title=A Collection of Treaties, Engagements and Sunnuds related to India and Neighbouring Countries|date=1909|location=Calcutta|page=185}}</ref>。二戰爆發，因鄰邦是[[義屬索馬利蘭|義屬索馬利蘭]]，又近印度洋，因此戰略位置很重要。1967年，索科特拉岛随[[南也门|南也门]]独立。目前，该岛是也门的领土。

2018年5月3日, 因於[[也门内战_(2015年至今)|也門內戰]]以致其政局不穩, [[阿聯酋|阿聯酋]]軍隊佔領該島, 並控制了島上機場。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/yemen-officials-say-emiratis-boost-forces-on-socotra-island/2018/05/02/84efa860-4e27-11e8-85c1-9326c4511033_story.html?utm_term=.31b060e05bdb|title=Yemen officials say Emiratis boost forces on Socotra island|website=The Washington Post|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2018-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508121347/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/yemen-officials-say-emiratis-boost-forces-on-socotra-island/2018/05/02/84efa860-4e27-11e8-85c1-9326c4511033_story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>稳定岛上局势后，阿联酋将该岛归还也门政府。

== 人口==
[[File:Airport_tower_(6408250813).jpg|缩略图]]塔台]]
岛上人口约5万人（2008年）<ref name = Reuters>[https://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSL23671476 FACTBOX-Socotra, jewel of biodiversity in Arabian Sea] {{Wayback|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSL23671476 |date=20210309020616 }}. Reuters, 2008-04-23</ref>，以[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]为主，也有少数居民来自索马里和印度<ref name="Xavier">{{cite book|first=Georg|last= Schurhammer|title=Francis Xavier; His Life, His Times: India, 1541–1544|volume= 2|publisher=Jesuit Historical Institute|year=1982|page=122}}</ref>，此外还有部分人被认为是非洲黑奴的后裔<ref name="Natvoltn">{{cite journal|editor-first= Norman|editor-last= Lockyer|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=qVEEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA575|journal= Nature|volume= 29|year= 1884|pages= 575–576|title= Socotra|doi= 10.1038/029575b0|issue= 755|access-date= 2017-09-05|archive-date= 2020-12-16|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201216224604/https://books.google.com/books?id=qVEEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA575|dead-url= no}}</ref>。该岛民族特有的“单倍型类群 J* (Y-DNA)”在全世界其他地方极为罕见，属于特有的[[人类Y染色体DNA单倍型类群|人类Y染色体DNA单倍型类群]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Černý|first1=Viktor|last2=Pereira|first2=Luísa|last3=Kujanová|first3=Martina|last4=Vašíková|first4=Alžběta|last5=Hájek|first5=Martin|last6=Morris|first6=Miranda|last7=Mulligan|first7=Connie J.|title=Out of Arabia—The settlement of Island Soqotra as revealed by mitochondrial and Y chromosome genetic diversity|journal=American Journal of Physical Anthropology|date=April 2009|volume=138|issue=4|doi=10.1002/ajpa.20960|pmid=19012329|url=https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Connie_Mulligan/publication/23476615_Out_of_Arabia-The_settlement_of_Island_Soqotra_as_revealed_by_mitochondrial_and_Y_chromosome_genetic_diversity/links/5653185908aefe619b18f505.pdf|access-date=2017-09-05|archive-date=2017-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905230617/https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Connie_Mulligan/publication/23476615_Out_of_Arabia-The_settlement_of_Island_Soqotra_as_revealed_by_mitochondrial_and_Y_chromosome_genetic_diversity/links/5653185908aefe619b18f505.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

当地语言为[[索科特拉语|索科特拉语]]。主要城镇[[哈迪布|哈迪布]]，有[[索科特拉機場|索科特拉機場]]，大部分班次都是飞往[[穆卡拉|穆卡拉]]，但由于[[沙特领导的干预也门行动|沙特阿拉伯的军事行动]]，索科特拉机场航线停飞<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ghattas|first1=Abir|title=Yemen's No Fly Zone: Thousands of Yemenis are Stranded Abroad|url=https://globalvoicesonline.org/2015/03/31/yemens-no-fly-zone-thousands-of-yemenis-are-stranded-abroad/#|accessdate=2015-04-08|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106080411/https://globalvoices.org/2015/03/31/yemens-no-fly-zone-thousands-of-yemenis-are-stranded-abroad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[枣椰|枣椰]]、[[烟草|烟草]]、畜牧业和渔业是岛上经济支柱。

==世界遗产==
索科特拉岛以“索科特拉群岛”为名，于2008年列入世界遗产。登录面积410,460 ha，缓冲区面积1,740,958 ha<ref>{{cite web|title=Socotra Archipelago|url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/1263|website=UNESCO World Heritage Centre|accessdate=2017-09-05|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225215843/http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/1263%20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。满足的世界遺產登錄基準是“拥有最重要及显著的多元性生物自然生态栖息地，包含从保育或科学的角度来看，符合普世价值的濒临绝种动物种。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sabanews.net/en/news151852.htm|title=EU to protect Socotra archipelago environment|publisher=Yemen News Agency (SABA)|work=Saba Net|date=2008-04-15|access-date=2017-09-05|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611234004/http://www.sabanews.net/en/news151852.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
